==Описание==

The {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignCenter.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignCenter|Spreadsheet AlignCenter]]}} tool makes the text inside the cell align to the center.

==Применение==

# Make sure there is an active {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|Spreadsheet]]}} open so that the button is enabled.
# Select a cell.
# Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignCenter.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignCenter|Spreadsheet AlignCenter]]}} button.


